data.description: RESERVE AT SOMERSET- Come see this Stunning Two Story 4 Bed 3.5 Bath home + Basement located in the desirable Center Grove School District! This home Features a Gourmet Kitchen, Quarts Countertops, Backsplash, Newley Built Bar in the Kitchen, and beautiful backyard with a Patio and Pond! The Master Bedroom includes a walk in Closet, Tile Shower & separate Garden Tub!  In the basement, there is a room that could be made into a 5th bedroom. The Neighborhood includes a Pool, Tennis Courts & Walking Trails! This Home won't last long!
